{
  "info": {
    "name": "Payment & Wallet Service",
    "description": "Local API collection for cosmicforge payment-wallet-service (port 8105).\n\nAll money values are kobo integers (1 NGN = 100 kobo). API base path: /api/v1/payment-wallet.\n\nAuth modes:\n- Customer endpoints: bearer token, role=customer, service=customer.\n- Provider endpoints: bearer token, service in {taxi, dispatch, hauling}, any non-empty role.\n- Internal endpoints: service-to-service HMAC (shared/go/serviceauth). The 'Internal (HMAC)' folder signs requests automatically via a pre-request script.\n- Webhook: Paystack x-paystack-signature (HMAC-SHA512 over raw body), signed manually.\n\nMint dev bearer tokens with: go run ./docs/devtoken -kind=customer (or -kind=provider -service=hauling). See docs/README.md.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
